      "questionText": "Evaluate 2⁵.",
      "options": [
        "10",
        "25",
        "32",
        "16"
      ],
      "correctAnswer": 2,
      "explanation": "2⁵ means 2 × 2 × 2 × 2 × 2, which equals 32. It is not 2 × 5."
